text.en:
2+ Level 9 monsters
This card gains the following effects based on the number of "Virtual World Gate" cards you control.
● 2+: This card can attack directly.
● 4: This card is unaffected by cards' activated effects, except "Virtual World" cards.
Once per turn (Quick Effect): You can detach 1 material from this card, then target 1 Effect Monster you control and 1 Effect Monster on the field with a different Attribute and Type; negate their effects until the end of this turn.
